extendedInfo.description: Download C programming practice test application to clear all concept of C.This app contains multiple choice questions of C to test programming skills. You can see your performance just by clicking submit. If you want to know explanation of questions, you can do that as well.This app will help students and professionals in their interviews, career growth and improving programming skills.The list of programs include basic programs like prime number program, factorial program , palindrome program and so on...install it and help comes handy in your preparation for tests, interviews and where ever you require...just one touch away.Keywords: Interview, C, C++, free, Multiple choice, questions, Programming, Assessment, Job, Skills, c programming test.
